    "Allāhumma Rabba hāżihid da'watit tāmmah, waṣ-ṣalātil qā'imah, āti Muḥammadanil wasīlata wal faḍīlah, wab'aṡhu maqāman maḥmūdanil lażī wa'adtah." : {

    },
